"Webhook Events\n\nBelow is the list of currently available webhook events.\n\nAccounts\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for accounts.\n\nThe recommended way to process this is to hit the retrieve an account API using the account_id from the webhook to check for account and data sync status.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nACCOUNTS.CONNECTED\tTriggered when a creator links a new work platform account.\nACCOUNTS.DISCONNECTED\tTriggered when a creator disconnects his work platform account.\n\nACCOUNTS.CONNECTED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"ACCOUNTS.CONNECTED\",\n  \"name\": \"account is connected\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"4544993eac6f4c4a9ec27e23f6cb8c56\",\n    \"user_id\": \"6bd84fa308f84e66abf108fd3d29f9ef\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T15:44:18.520054\"\n  }\n}\n\nACCOUNTS.DISCONNECTED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"ACCOUNTS.DISCONNECTED\",\n  \"name\": \"account is disconnected\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"29ebb0d8296b45159753833989834dbd\",\n    \"user_id\": \"1290a1f5ad9b48b5a3f10daaa26469fd\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T16:12:58.006355\"\n  }\n}\nProfiles\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for profiles.\n\nThe recommended way to process this is to hit the retrieve a profile API using the profile_id from the webhook to get the latest identity data for the given profile.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nPROFILES.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator profile is synced successfully.\nPROFILES.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator profile is updated.\n\nPROFILES.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"PROFILES.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"profile added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"4544993eac6f4c4a9ec27e23f6cb8c56\",\n    \"user_id\": \"6bd84fa308f84e66abf108fd3d29f9ef\",\n    \"profile_id\": \"74e5f67b9df04cbeba0894d749561447\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T12:59:51.874364\"\n  }\n}\n\nPROFILES.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"PROFILES.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"profile updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"711c36fccb2b4304afb4bcd14e6bfbdd\",\n    \"user_id\": \"0e3808ca12174c0082381fc5653f9538\",\n    \"profile_id\": \"bdec2a8924d14904b022b90c8a463559\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:11.304556\"\n  }\n}\nProfile Audience\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for the profile audience.\n\nThe recommended way to process this is to hit the retrieve audience demographics API using the account_id from the webhook to get the latest audience demographics data for the given account.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nPROFILES_AUDIENCE.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's audience demographics is scanned successfully.\nPROFILES_AUDIENCE.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator's audience demographics is updated.\n\nPROFILES_AUDIENCE.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"PROFILES_AUDIENCE.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"profile audience added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"profile_id\": \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25T16:45:26.761Z\"\n  }\n}\n\nPROFILES_AUDIENCE.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"PROFILES_AUDIENCE.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"profile audience updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"profile_id\": \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25T16:45:26.761Z\"\n  }\n}\nContent\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for content.\n\nContent webhooks may deliver a maximum of up to 100 content IDs in the items array. The recommended way to process this is to hit the retrieve content items in bulk API, using the content IDs listed in the items array from the webhook to get the latest content data for the given IDs. Ideally, this should be done using a messaging queue system while respecting rate limits.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nCONTENTS.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's content is scanned successfully .\nCONTENTS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator's content is updated.\n\nCONTENTS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"CONTENTS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"contents added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25 16:45:26.761622\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nCONTENTS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"CONTENTS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"contents updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25 16:45:26.761622\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\nContent Comments\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for content comments.\n\nThe recommended way to process this is to hit the retrieve all comments API, using the account_id and content IDs listed in the items array from the webhook to get the latest comment data for the given account and content ID. Ideally, this should be done using a messaging queue system while respecting rate limits.\n\nThe item IDs given in the payload are the content IDs for which the corresponding comments have been added or updated.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nCONTENTS_COMMENTS.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's content is scanned for comments successfully .\nCONTENTS_COMMENTS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a comment on any content is updated.\n\nCONTENTS_COMMENTS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"CONTENTS_COMMENTS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"contents comments added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25 16:45:26.761622\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nCONTENTS_COMMENTS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"CONTENTS_COMMENTS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"contents comments updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25 16:45:26.761622\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\nContent Groups\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for content groups.\n\nContent group webhooks may deliver a maximum of up to 100 content group IDs in the items array. The recommended way to process this is to hit the retrieve content group items in bulk API, using the content-group IDs listed in the items array from the webhook to get the latest content-group data for the given IDs. Ideally, this should be done using a messaging queue system while respecting rate limits.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nCONTENT-GROUPS.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's content group i.e. playlists, albums is scanned successfully .\nCONTENT-GROUPS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator's content group i.e. playlists, albums is updated.\n\nCONTENT-GROUPS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"CONTENT-GROUPS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"content groups added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25 16:45:26.761622\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nCONTENT-GROUPS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"CONTENT-GROUPS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"content groups updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"2b3316b8f4684f03841140b547ec7eb3\",\n    \"user_id\": \"9864110df20646d29860d0f687c2670d\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-10-25 16:45:26.761622\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\nIncome\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for income.\n\nIncome webhooks may deliver a maximum of up to 100 IDs in the items array. The recommended way to process this is to hit the \"retrieve in bulk API\" of the associated resource type, such as retrieve social transactions in bulk API, using the transaction IDs listed in the items array from the webhook to get the latest transaction data for the given IDs. The resource type can be identified from the webhook event name and the category (social, commerce, etc.) can be identified using the account_id in the webhook payload. Ideally, this should be done using a messaging queue system while respecting rate limits.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nTRANSACTIONS.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's new transactions are scanned successfully.\nTRANSACTIONS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator's existing transactions are updated.\nPAYOUTS.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's new payouts are scanned successfully.\nPAYOUTS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator's existing payouts are updated.\nBALANCES.ADDED\tTriggered when a creator's new balances are scanned successfully.\nBALANCES.UPDATED\tTriggered when a creator's existing balances are updated.\n\nTRANSACTIONS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"TRANSACTIONS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"transactions added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nTRANSACTIONS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"TRANSACTIONS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"transactions updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nPAYOUTS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"PAYOUTS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"payouts added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nPAYOUTS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"PAYOUTS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"payouts updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nBALANCES.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"BALANCES.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"balances added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nBALANCES.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"BALANCES.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"balances updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\nActivity\n\nThe table below lists the webhook events available for activity.\n\nActivity webhooks may deliver a maximum of up to 100 IDs in the items array. The recommended way to process this is to hit the \"retrieve in bulk API\" of the associated resource type, such as retrieve artists in bulk API, using the artist IDs listed in the items array from the webhook to get the latest data for the given IDs. Ideally, this should be done using a messaging queue system while respecting rate limits.\n\nWEBHOOK EVENT\tDESCRIPTION\nACTIVITY-ARTISTS.ADDED\tTriggered when a user's new artists' data is scanned successfully.\nACTIVITY-ARTISTS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a user's existing artists' data is updated.\nACTIVITY-CONTENTS.ADDED\tTriggered when a user's new contents' data is scanned successfully.\nACTIVITY-CONTENTS.UPDATED\tTriggered when a user's existing contents' data is updated.\n\nACTIVITY-ARTISTS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"ACTIVITY-ARTISTS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"artists added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nACTIVITY-ARTISTS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"ACTIVITY-ARTISTS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"artists updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nACTIVITY-CONTENTS.ADDED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"ACTIVITY-CONTENTS.ADDED\",\n  \"name\": \"contents added\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb1744bcf9dd6f90548af9089\",\n    \"last_updated_time\": \"2021-11-10T10:09:09.704257\",\n    \"items\": [\n      \"0ccc5adf0d7d4eaabca56b58420f7da7\",\n      \"27c01cb47d3f462eaba08a86dc7bab82\",\n      \"c61610a33ca641caaec8f2655c1d49f8\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\nACTIVITY-CONTENTS.UPDATED\n\n{\n  \"event\": \"ACTIVITY-CONTENTS.UPDATED\",\n  \"name\": \"contents updated\",\n  \"id\": \"674c9030-640a-4c83-a680-666361044f67\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"account_id\": \"f9ed198434094d498473953cade79f5e\",\n    \"user_id\": \"8145c37cb174